OL,6,FBut can you imagine the accusations
OL,7,Fof a cover-up if this story ` and the
OL,8,Fawful situation on social media ` had
OL,9,Fbeen ignored while it was being
OL,10,Fcovered extensively elsewhere?
OL,12,FThere must be ways found to protect
OL,13,Fcompletely innocent parties from this
OL,14,Fkind of terrible speculation. But how
OL,15,Fdo you do this if people are posting
OL,16,Flies anonymously?
OL,18,FIt is all so complex. Beware of
OL,19,Fanyone offering more than their
OL,20,Fopinion on these issues. There is no
OL,21,Fsimple solution to an unprecedented
OL,22,Fproblem.
OL,3,CThe difficult questions arising from
OL,4,Cthe Huw Edwards story
