OL,6,FAnd what of BBC News?
OL,8,FIt is incredibly hard for them to
OL,9,Freport on such a story when it
OL,10,Fconcerns a colleague.
OL,12,FAnd is there any way back for Huw
OL,13,FEdwards once he is better and if
OL,14,Fnothing happens to re-ignite this
OL,15,Fstory?
OL,17,FIt seems terrible to think of a
OL,18,Fcareer being destroyed if there has
OL,19,Fbeen no illegality. Let he who is
OL,20,Fwithout sin.
OL,3,CThe difficult questions arising from
OL,4,Cthe Huw Edwards story
