OL,6,FThese are the kind of questions which
OL,7,Fwill be discussed.
OL,9,FThere are no simple answers. I merely
OL,10,Fpose questions and hopefully there
OL,11,Fcan be calm and reasonable
OL,12,Fdiscussions after the dust settles.
OL,14,FAs a general point of principle, we
OL,15,Fneed to be very careful about any
OL,16,Fattacks on well-known figures in any
OL,17,Fwalk of life unless they are found to
OL,18,Fhave broken the law or actively
OL,19,Fdeceived the public.
OL,3,CThe difficult questions arising from
OL,4,Cthe Huw Edwards story
