OL,6,FBut all those in positions of power
OL,7,For trust should be aware of how that
OL,8,Fpower (even unintentionally) can be
OL,9,Fmisused even without illegality.
OL,11,FIt is all so terrible for all
OL,12,Fconcerned. There are no winners here.
